            name: Frisia
            version: v4
            authors: abductedPlatypus
            description: "This coastal area, spanning current day Dutch and German coasts, is surrounded by islands connected to land by shallow wads.             description: >-
              Bog spawns players on opposite sides of the map to each other,

            version: '1.0'
            authors: Corn
            description: "This map was specially designed for FFA King of The Hill games. \r\nEvery player's base looks like an apartment, separated from other lands with a strip of forest . It opens with cutting toward the map centre. In the centre of the map there is a round swampy lake, where the monument appears when King of the Hill mode is set.
